657
00:46:43,670 --> 00:46:45,604
He wasn't drunk.
Ray fell asleep at the wheel.

658
00:46:45,672 --> 00:46:48,197
-- Is he okay?
-- Yeah.

659
00:46:48,275 --> 00:46:51,403
That was the first thing
