Dr. Bimbu, one of the
authors of the book --

711
00:50:14,614 --> 00:50:15,672
-- Bimbu?
-- Dad.

712
00:50:15,749 --> 00:50:17,114
I just asked his name.

713
00:50:17,183 --> 00:50:18,775
You had a tone.

714
00:50:20,387 --> 00:50:24,346
He said there are two
reasons why extraterrestrials
would visit us --

715
00:50:24,424 --> 00:50:26,949
