harvest our planet next.

720
00:50:39,906 --> 00:50:41,533
Here.

721
00:51:10,870 --> 00:51:13,930
<i>Looks a little like</i>
<i>our house, doesn't it?</i>

722
00:51:14,007 --> 00:51:16,373
<i>Same windows.</i>

723
00:51:16,443 --> 00:51:18,070
